15 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
16 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law not to be
17 codified in the Oklahoma Statutes reads as follows:
18 There is hereby appropriated to the Oklahoma Opioid Abatement
19 Revolving Fund created pursuant to Section 30.6 of Title 74 of the
20 Oklahoma Statutes, from any monies not otherwise appropriated from
21 the Opioid Lawsuit Settlement Fund (Fund 383) of the State Treasury,
22 the sum of Twenty Million Dollars ($20,000,000.00) to be budgeted
23 and expended in accordance with law.
